fields.title: Inception
fields.description: A thief who enters the dreams of others to steal their secrets.

fields.title: The Shawshank Redemption
fields.description: Two imprisoned men bond over several years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

fields.title: The Dark Knight
fields.description: When the menace known as the Joker emerges from his mysterious past, he wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham.

fields.title: Pulp Fiction
fields.description: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster and his wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.

fields.title: Forrest Gump
fields.description: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the Vietnam War, the Watergate scandal, and other historical events unfold from the perspective of an Alabama man with an IQ of 75.

fields.title: The Godfather
fields.description: An organized crime dynasty's aging patriarch transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant son.

fields.title: The Matrix
fields.description: A computer hacker learns from mysterious rebels about the true nature of his reality and his role in the war against its controllers.

fields.title: Titanic
fields.description: A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.

fields.title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
fields.description: A quest to destroy the One Ring that has the power to bring about the downfall of its creator, the dark lord Sauron.

fields.title: The Silence of the Lambs
fields.description: A young FBI cadet must receive the help of an incarcerated and manipulative cannibal killer to help catch another serial killer, a madman who skins his victims.

fields.title: Interstellar
fields.description: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.
